Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.05,0:23:54.96,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1060,550)}{\fad(1080,0)}恋爱是盲目的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.01,0:24:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45}hi 我是Tiger&Bunny中总是在入睡前喝杯牛奶的那位 巴纳比是也
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.78,0:24:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？空天先生陷入爱河？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.04,0:24:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可是大事件的预感！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.06,0:24:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 基友英雄传
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.83,0:24:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The sky's the limit 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.22,0:24:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,see you~
